\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Vision (one line)
\f1\b0 \uc0\u8232 Help solo real estate agents build businesses that feel human while creating stability for their practice.\

\f0\b Mission
\f1\b0 \uc0\u8232 Deliver invisible infrastructure that quietly organizes an agent\'92s past clients into a stewarded network \'97 relieving mental load, preserving relationships, and enabling calm, intentional outreach.\

\f0\b Design Principles
\f1\b0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Start minimal: deliver relief immediately. One mic-drop moment (cleaned import + insight).\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Human-first voice: every customer-facing message reads like the agent wrote it.\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Agent-as-hero: agent branding is front-and-center; platform is invisible.\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Predictable, not pulsing: quarterly cadence + rare meaningful triggers.\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Premium feel through restraint: fewer features, superb polish.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 MVP Success Criteria
\f1\b0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Agent can upload messy CSV \uc0\u8594  system normalizes & returns a clean dataset within the prototype flow.\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Agent sees immediate insight: households count + \'93X entering 5\'967yr window\'94 message.\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Agent can review the touchpoints queue and send one-click message to homeowners (via push/email/SMS).\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Property Value Updates meter visible, with add-on flow simulated.\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Homeowner receives push/SMS/email with link to a single-screen deeper insight (no required login).\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa321\partightenfactor0

